municipalities
Class MunicipalitiesRecord

java.lang.Object
  municipalities.MunicipalitiesRecord

public class MunicipalitiesRecord
extends java.lang.Object

MunicipalitiesRecord contains a set of Municipality and is used to manage, access and search them.
